# compareSuggestions

Compares suggestions.

## Parameters

| Param | Type                            | Description            |
| ----- | ------------------------------- | ---------------------- |
| a     | `compareSuggestions~Suggestion` | the first suggestion.  |
| b     | `compareSuggestions~Suggestion` | the second suggestion. |

## Returns

`number` - the comparison result.

## Example

```js
import {compareSuggestions} from '@bluecateng/pelagos';

const suggestions = generateSuggestions().sort(compareSuggestions);
```

## Other types

### compareSuggestions~Suggestion

`Object` - a suggestion.

#### Properties

| Name  | Type     | Description                     |
| ----- | -------- | ------------------------------- |
| order | `number` | the priority of the suggestion. |
| name  | `string` | the displayed name.             |
